{
  "texts": [
    "Leader-member exchange (LMX) is affected by the structural differences of individuals measured by the degree of centrality in the advice network 99.",
    "LMX has a reciprocal correlation with job satisfaction 100 and turnover 101.",
    "The ranking position in the communication network 16 and the friendship network 17 has an important effect on the turnover decision.",
    "The emotional and friendship dimensions of relationships influence the LMX 102.",
    "The so-called \"density of multiplex networks\" indicates the cohesion of management and affects the team performance 97."
  ]
}